Beatrice Shongwe, News24 Correspondent(File) Multimedia &nbsp; &nbsp; User Galleries &nbsp; &nbsp; News in Pictures Send us your pictures &nbsp; &nbsp; Send us your stories Mbombela - The personal assistant of JS Moroka municipality's Mayor Gimani Mahlangu was found shot dead in his rental home last week, police said on Wednesday.Neighbours found Nicholus Mapayane Peu, 41, in his rented home in Kameelrivier A, Vaalbank, last Wednesday around 21:00, Brigadier Leonard Hlathi said.Peu&rsquo;s car was missing, and the garage door was wide open. He had several bullet wounds. The house had been ransacked and clothes were scattered everywhere. His grey VW Polo was later found abandoned in Kameelrivier B, with the keys inside.Police were still searching for the killers. 24.com encourages commentary submitted via MyNews24. Contributions of 200 words or more will be considered for publication.